bilingual.source: One Lehman executive says the firm determined sometime the prior night that additional capital wouldn't be needed because Lehman hoped to raise more money by selling additional assets.
bilingual.target: 一位雷曼兄弟的高管说，该公司在前一晚上决定无需筹集更多的资金，因为该公司希望通过出售更多的资产筹资。

bilingual.source: Previously there's been an accounting error: land use change has been left out of prior analysis.
bilingual.target: 以前人们都算错了一本账：在前期分析时都把土地使用的改变忽略不计了。

bilingual.source: It is schisms, which involve the skipping over of a particular segment of prior initiation and the associated genetic materials that can lead to disease if not rectified.
bilingual.target: 正是分裂，包括在前期提升中跳过某特定片段及相关遗传资料，如果不纠正的话就会带来疾病。

bilingual.source: Their decisions agree without prior consultation, without prior discussion.
bilingual.target: 他们的决定不谋而合，没有事先讨论过。

bilingual.source: We need to plan this trip prior.
bilingual.target: 我们需要预先计划好这次旅行。
他预先准备好了所有材料。
上一个项目已经完成了。

bilingual.source: They have prior matters to attend to.
bilingual.target: 他们有更重要的事情要处理。
上一个会议讨论了这个问题。

bilingual.source: You should learn about this project prior.
bilingual.target: 你应该预先了解一下这个项目。

list.abstract: prior（英 [ˈpraɪə]，美 [ˈpraɪər]），英语单词，作形容词为在先的；在前的；居先的。作名词为犯罪前科；男主持；男修道院副院长。例句：It will settle the prior controversies.（它将解决之前的争议。） prior的近义词有preferred、underlying、before、antecedently。

yingyinNormal.en: Sue them for prior restraint. What does that mean?
yingyinNormal.zh: 起诉他们先行制止。那是什么意思？

yingyinNormal.en: A company I bought into prior to gonna work at Witter.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是我加入迪安维特公司之前买进的公司。

yingyinNormal.en: But Fire King has a prior commitment. His herd needs him.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但火焰王有别的承诺 这里的同伙需要他。

yingyinNormal.en: The recent transfers of Beatrice and Caleb Prior, children of Andrew Prior, call into question the soundness of Abnegation's teachings and values.
yingyinNormal.zh: 近日离开的安德鲁普赖尔的一对儿女碧翠斯普赖尔和迦勒普赖尔引发了人们对无私派教育方法和价值观的怀疑。

yingyinNormal.en: Prior to midnight we then run this wire from the tree to the water.
yingyinNormal.zh: 午夜之前我们用这段电线连接闪电树和水。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, the government can't ban the expression of an idea prior to its publication.
yingyinNormal.zh: 政府不能在一个想法公开之前禁止对它的表达。

yingyinNormal.en: And I'm sure you don't know who you can trust, and all prior authentications may be compromised. So, I offer you this.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你现在肯定不知道应该要相信谁，此前的身份验证可能都被动了手脚，所以…我用了这个证明。

yingyinNormal.en: What questions did you ask them? I was trying to determine if anyone had prior knowledge of the flaws in the Lobera .38.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你问了他们哪些问题？我想确定是否有人事先已知罗布拉点38式手枪存在缺陷。

yingyinNormal.en: My colleagues and I are mapping the neurological substrates that subserve global information processing, which is required for all cognitive reasoning, including scientific inquiry, making my research ipso facto prior in the ordo cognoscendi.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我和同事们正在绘制神经基质，有利于促进全球信息处理，这种研究既要求认知推理也包括科学探索，由此事实可见，我的研究在认知序列上更高一层。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全四级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

derivative_info_list.mean: v. 优先考虑；给… 以优先权；确定优先次序；按优先顺序列出
n. 优先考虑的事；优先；重点；优先通行权

word_family.mean: adj. 在先的；在前的；居先的；先前的

sense_info_list.en: existing or coming before in time; order; importance

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Prior</highlight> to being spoon-fed number words, children can only approximately discriminate quantities beyond three.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在被灌输数字单词之前，孩子们只能大致区分超过三的数量。

examination_example.sentence: Recently, the U.S. market has grown to 263,000 bikes, a 25% gain from the <highlight>prior</highlight> year.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 最近，美国市场的自行车数量已经增长到了263,000辆，比去年增长了25%。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Prior</highlight> to the new study, little was known about the risks of getting directly infected by common respiratory viruses, such as the flu or common cold, on an airplane, the researchers said.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 研究人员说，在这项新研究之前，人们对在飞机上直接感染诸如流感或普通感冒等常见呼吸道病毒的风险知之甚少。

sense_info_list.en: before a particular time or event

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Prior</highlight> to beginning his design, the architect spent some time in the client's old home.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在开始设计之前，建筑师在客户的老房子里待了一段时间。

examination_example.sentence: Technical engineers who worked on the plane <highlight>prior</highlight> to take-off are reportedly going to be questioned by the police.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 据报道，在飞机起飞前在飞机上工作的技术工程师将受到警方的讯问。
